---

Optimize React Application

1. Component Level Optimization

- Use keys for list
- React.memo - HOC - To memorize component- If props change then only render the component
- useMemo - Hooks - Memorize heavy calculation - Calculate only when specified prop is changed.
- useCallback - Hooks - Memorize the callback function

2. App Level

- Lazy Loading
- Treeshaking - Remove unused code
- Minification - Remove whitespaces, rename variable
- Compression -
  https://medium.com/@shivalkondwar1/boost-your-react-components-a-beginners-guide-to-react-memo-usememo-and-usecallback-13de63d936f5
